OL,7,FIt used to be how Samantha Forster
OL,8,Fwould get out and about, but since her
OL,9,Fenergy bills skyrocketed she has been
OL,10,Fnot able to repair or charge it.
OL,12,FWhen I visited her at home she told me
OL,13,Fthe impact on her life had been
OL,14,Fdramatic.
OL,16,FShe's now pretty much housebound.
OL,18,FIn thethe chancellor promised to look
OL,19,Fat bringing in a cap on the energy
OL,20,Ftariff paid by vulnerable households.
